    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather upholstery and trim showing virtually no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a complete service history. Every feature and electronic system functions exactly as intended, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from a brand-new car. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved example.",
