      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specimen, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque vectoring through the corners. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from preventative subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension setup featuring Bilstein dampers. Recent critical maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and a recent valve adjustment, ensuring the valvetrain operates with factory precision. While showing the honest patina of a well-loved driver, its mechanical integrity is paramount, offering the visceral, linear throttle response and 50/50 weight distribution that defined an era of motorsport engineering.",
